com.fico.streamvar.api.record

Interface TerminationNotice

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseErrorResponse

    public interface TerminationNotice
    Marker interface to denote output records. When the output class of a model step extends AbstractRecord and implements TerminationNotice, the model executor will short circuit model execution for that input transaction
